{"tid":230134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乜市民唔捐血就會令到血庫存量不足咁兒戲","createTime":"2017-05-05T06:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T08:51:26.000Z","uid":67347,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a222773a9492e8834a793dc547be395efa73b436","tid":230134,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"呢d乜道理黎？<br />\n政府唔駛做野架？<br />\n有乜理由旨意哂市民去捐<br />\n唔夠咪去買囉on99<br />\n政府咁多錢<br />\n慈善團體叫人捐錢之餘都會問政府拎啦"},{"pid":"44969bf436ba370fbbc165ed733f2f47cea49cc5","tid":230134,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"咁捐法多多血都唔夠你用啦"},{"pid":"b402c3a0e04d5a2e1d64ff5a18a3b6962d20fd85","tid":230134,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"咁政府咪可以去大陸買番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba123546ce16fcfb065bb7711911d5d96315c73","tid":230134,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁政府咪可以去大陸買番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係ga<br />\n買返自己捐上去d血<br />\n但都唔係一味叫人捐血<br />\n又唔諗其他方法<br />\n今年已經緊急呼籲左幾次"},{"pid":"5dcc422fc47e79530d7a57f592971f02b9a411b3","tid":230134,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"你知唔知買賣血液幾恐怖，衍生既社會問題幾嚴重？"},{"pid":"aba76a641fb7a174d1b0df0dbda0adc0db0c638c","tid":230134,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你知唔知買賣血液幾恐怖，衍生既社會問題幾嚴重？</blockquote><br />\n唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f2b4cd459c0b425632f17c5299fe624fedf0b3","tid":230134,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你知唔知買賣血液幾恐怖，衍生既社會問題幾嚴重？</blockquote><br />\n咁當然唔係政府向市民買<br />\n係政府同政府買"},{"pid":"7a4fbfb88dffd33fe916678e058544